## Frameworks and Tools Supporting Resource Allocation

### Responsibility Assignment Matrix (RAM) and RACI Matrix

Project managers use tools like the Responsibility Assignment Matrix (RAM) and RACI matrix to clarify roles and responsibilities, reducing conflicts and ensuring accountability ([Project Risk Coach, n.d.](https://projectriskcoach.com/develop-resource-management-plan/)).

| RACI Role     | Description                                         |
|---------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| Responsible   | Person(s) who perform the work                      |
| Accountable   | Person who owns the work and approves completion   |
| Consulted     | Subject-matter experts consulted during execution  |
| Informed      | Individuals kept informed of progress and decisions|

These tools help project managers allocate human resources effectively by defining who does what and ensuring clarity in resource usage.

### Resource Management Software

Modern project management increasingly relies on software tools to:

- Track resource availability and workload in real-time.
- Prevent over-allocation and burnout.
- Adjust resource plans dynamically in response to project changes ([Asana, 2021](https://asana.com/resources/resource-allocation)).

